{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"212f1ea659","title":"现阶段国内的主要矛盾","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"28835332b4","index":0,"year":1952,"month":6,"day":6,"articleId":"212f1ea659"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji6","name":"毛泽东文集第六卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives9/main/books/wenji6.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji6":{"comments":[{"id":"92ee6b27b1","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659","index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据手稿刊印。"},{"id":"b8b447a7ee","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659","index":1,"part_index":0,"offset":10,"text":"这是毛泽东在中共中央《关于民主党派工作的决定（草稿）》上写的批语。"},{"id":"71fede30b8","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659","index":2,"part_index":1,"offset":2,"text":"罗迈，即李维汉（一八九六——一九八四），湖南长沙人。当时任中共中央统战部部长。"},{"id":"2ac616e853","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659","index":3,"part_index":2,"offset":9,"text":"毛泽东的修改，主要是将中共中央《关于民主党派工作的决定（草稿）》中的“中间阶级”、“中间阶层”的提法，改为“资产阶级、城市上层小资产阶级（即雇有少数几个工人或店员的小资本家）、一部分从地主阶级分化出来带有资本主义色彩的分子以及和这些阶级、阶层相联系的知识分子”。"}],"contents":[{"id":"77e9183a60","type":"title","text":"现阶段国内的主要矛盾","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659"},{"id":"b8b447a7ee","type":"appellation","text":"罗迈同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659"},{"id":"71fede30b8","type":"paragraph","text":"此件已阅，略有修改，请再酌。在打倒地主阶级和官僚资产阶级以后，中国内部的主要矛盾即是工人阶级与民族资产阶级的矛盾，故不应再将民族资产阶级称为中间阶级。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659"},{"id":"2ac616e853","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659"},{"id":"c0a156e774","type":"paragraph","text":"六月六日上午三时","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659"}],"page":{"id":"481ce0ee3c","publicationId":"wenji6","articleId":"212f1ea659","start":245,"end":245}}}},"__N_SSG":true}